name: When the sun goes down
description: Hic saves  There’s a rooftop I love to climb. It has a really good view of the downtown below and it gives me vibes from the original BladeRunner movie. I took this photo when it was raining, just like the movie. Looking down the city on a rainy night, it gives me strange feelings, feelings that I haven’t had before.  / Format : JPEG / Size : 3376 x 6000
